{"tid":2037619,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一條膠管，判三個月","createTime":"2020-05-27T05:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T11:33:16.000Z","uid":211994,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"290e695c8f8fb08daf060e666bcfe65b842b0b45","tid":2037619,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200527&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60986000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200527%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60986000&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=772b3365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200527%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60986000&h=953c6bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200527&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60986000</a><br />\n<br />\n去年9月有組織發起「光復屯門公園」遊行，公開大學女生當日被搜出管有一條90厘米長的膠管，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。案件原定今早開審，女生突然認罪，求情透露當時只是為陌生人保管膠管，沒有堵路或襲警行為。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啓亮指，相信被告年輕有為，亦是有抱負及理念的年輕人，而涉案物品只是一條膠管，沒有用以攻擊任何人；惟基於《公安條例》所限，判刑選擇不多，考慮後以入獄四個月為量刑起點，並給予四分之一刑期扣減後，判被告入獄三個月。"},{"pid":"0c6aa7d9fd039d44499e91c3e473c9147ad8093a","tid":2037619,"uid":1550,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"弱撚智"},{"pid":"f9a14f0fd94f44febdbc322c0a2d04c990cc2370","tid":2037619,"uid":187664,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"認罪...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8626f4b5c717a991bd53aabfdecb94a813c9f1","tid":2037619,"uid":137871,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"我諗經過呢一戰之後，好多人唔會再咁易對坐過監既人有偏見"},{"pid":"f70c524e0f7cccab8a08ff6c1d32441b5c46fa8b","tid":2037619,"uid":124,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"因為佢認罪。。。不過專重當時人"},{"pid":"4b81be8196efc87a8e34fa61f1face92d92e4180